org.apache.paimon.data.columnar

Class ColumnarRowIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.utils.RecyclableIterator<InternalRow>
      • org.apache.paimon.data.columnar.ColumnarRowIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileRecordIterator<InternalRow>, RecordReader.RecordIterator<InternalRow>, VectorizedRecordIterator

    public class ColumnarRowIterator
extends RecyclableIterator<InternalRow>
implements FileRecordIterator<InternalRow>, VectorizedRecordIterator
    A RecordReader.RecordIterator that returns InternalRows. The next row is set by ColumnarRow.setRowId(int).
